            profile, and power up your quests.
          </p>
          <img src="./images/Inspiration3.png" alt="inspiration" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Div Container for Features Section -->
    <div class="py-24 mt-48 mb-48 flex flex-col" id="features">
      <!-- Features Title -->
      <h2 class="font-combo text-4xl text-center">Features</h2>
      <div class="flex justify-evenly">
        <!-- Features Text and Image 1 -->
        <div class="mb-24 text-center">
          <h3 class="text-2xl">üõ°Ô∏è Personalized Hero Paths</h3>
          <p>
            Choose your self-help focus‚Äîlike productivity, mindfulness, or energy‚Äîand get tasks and monsters tailored to your path.
          </p>
